    "Furthermore, when a person is removed from the initialization process in order to generate a new one, the course does not alter; rather, a new person is created by altering every dimension.",
    "The two stages of the GBSO strategy are as follows: the first stage concentrates on genetic selection through the use of the breeder genetic algorithm (BGA) mutation, crossover through extended initial mating, and stochastic universal sampling (SUS) method.",
